[OVERLAY] VimFu — gh — Select Mode
[SAY] G H starts select mode character wise. It works like visual mode, but typing replaces the selection. Like how selection works in normal text editors.
[SAY] Go to red. Select it with v 2 l.
[KEYS] '2Gf"l'
[OVERLAY] 2Gf"l  on red

